# Random Color Changer

This project is a simple JavaScript application that changes the background color and the text color of the body to a random color when a button is clicked. It is built using HTML, SCSS, and vanilla JavaScript.

## Features

- Generates a random color on each button click
- Dynamically updates the background color and text color of the body using JavaScript
- Clean and simple user interface
- Uses proper DOM manipulation and event handling

## Technologies Used

- HTML
- SCSS
- JavaScript

## How It Works

- A button click triggers a JavaScript
